extendedInfo.description: The Travel Schedules application is a comprehensive guide to Train, Bus, Boat schedules for the Pearl River Delta Area including Guangzhou, Shenzhen, Zhuhai, Macau and Hong KongThis application is developed for the Kingdom of the Netherlands to provide and support business opportunities in South China for Dutch companies
